Thoughts on AI generated images? 🤔🤔🤔

Artificial Intelligence (AI) generated images have been popping on my feed lately and got me curious. Shown here are just quick samples of what a few prompts had spit out using StableDiffusion for the 1st time. Nothing to feel threatened by, especially looking at the last 2 slides 😂😂😂 

But there have been some really good ones I’ve seen elsewhere that got me thinking if we as Artists are about to loose some opportunities because of this new process. 😓Or is it just another tool we can use to our advantage. 🤨

Very curious to hear what you guys think. GO!!

@meguiars to the rescue 💛🖤

Quick update on the E36, it’s looking like it’s old self once again lol! No more barn find steeze 😜

During the process of getting the car running, the car sat outside at the shop, long enough to where water spots were etched into the paint 🫠💦 I tried washing it thinking it wasn’t so bad but man it was baked in there. Tried distilled water / vinegar mix and other popular google result solutions but nothing worked. 🥵🥵🥵 Was quoted $1500 to get it professionally removed 😳😵. 

Finally consulted Nick at @meguiars and had some good results with their Ultimate Compound - but being applied by hand, it would’ve taken a few days just to do the hood. @meguiars very own Mike Pennington and Derek @detail_werks offered to check out the damage in person.  They came prepared with much stronger stuff - 110 Ultra Pro Compound applied with MT300 DA Polisher and 3-in-1 Liquid Wax to finish it off 💫💫💫 

So thrilled with the results, thought all hope was lost but not a single water spots left 😍😍 and the full exterior done in 2hrs. 💨💨 This is just Phase 1 apparently lol. Will be dropping off the car at their HQ to get some deep cleaning and detailing soon. 🔜 But first, time to finally enjoy and drive this thing again! 🥳 #jonsibal

Last Evolution #cossievo86 

Was excited to get a text from @iamstanchen when he picked up this 190e project early last yr - apparently his “last build” lol. 

Just as it was on his #crazy88m3 project, my part of the project was to mock it up based on his vision with the correct exterior updates and design a wheel that’s true to its era. We came up with this 5-spoke design as an homage to the original Penta wheels, a reimagined multi-pc design with modern styling cues and hidden hardware to stay true the original look. Props as always to the wizards at @rotiform for the execution. 💯

Some details like the DTM mirrors, the interior updates, @mountune_usa built engine complete with cf velocity stacks were 👌🏾 Glad to see this build come together, credit to @smokedogg_customs .

I doubt this will be Stan’s last build lol 😆 but you can catch it this weekend at the Golden Era event hosted by @toyotires .

Golden Era 🔑

Was great to take part in the @toyotires Golden Era event yesterday celebrating the 80’s-90’s BMW, Benz and Audi held at the @ancillarystudios . 🙌🏽

That era was the key that got me obsessed with European cars watching hours of DTM and BTCC super touring race cars recorded in my VHS tapes 📼📼📼, and going to import shows where a few Euro dominated the scene 🏆🏆🏆. I still remember ZZAD, D2 Technik, CEC, and Wheel Power bringing the heat back then.🔥🔥🔥

So it’s pretty cool to see a niche event getting these cars together once again mixed with some period correct and modern builds. 💫 Props to @iamstanchen , @periodcorrect , @kw_suspension @leencustoms and @motulusa 👏🏾👏🏾👏🏾 More pics in my IG story.
